These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: soy-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate, juice
Pet: guinea-pig, pony, bird, frog
1. Pet:frog is on the left of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
2. Beverage:soy-milk is on the left of Pet:pony##1
3. Beverage:juice is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:bird is on the left or right of Pet:frog##3
5. Beverage:soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta | juice | hot-chocolate |
| Pet        | guinea-pig | pony   | frog | bird    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: action, epic, documentary, family
Nationality: mexican, canadian, pakistani, indonesian
1. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left of Movie-Genre:family##1
2. Nationality:mexican is on the left of Nationality:pakistani##1
3. Nationality:pakistani is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:mexican == Movie-Genre:action##1
5. Nationality:canadian is on the right of Nationality:pakistani##1
6. Nationality:mexican == Movie-Genre:action##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  | epic  | family |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | mexican | pakistani | canadian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: banana, broccoli, spinach, radish
Movie-Genre: scientific, disaster, thriller, comedy
1. Food:radish is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:comedy##3
2. Food:spinach is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the left or right of Food:broccoli##3
4. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the right of Movie-Genre:thriller##1
5. Movie-Genre:scientific is in an odd position##4
6. Food:broccoli is on the right of Food:spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | radish | spinach | broccoli    | banana      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller        | comedy     | scientific | disaster |

