.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: photography, puzzles, board-games, skydiving
Music-Genre: electronic, salsa, pop, jazz
1. Hobby:puzzles is between Music-Genre:electronic and Music-Genre:jazz##2
2. Hobby:skydiving is on the left of Hobby:photography##1
3. Music-Genre:pop is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:salsa is on the left of Music-Genre:jazz##1
5. Music-Genre:salsa is on the right of Hobby:photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | photography | puzzles | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic   | salsa    | jazz  |

