2. Nationality:spanish == Music-Genre:house##1
3. Nationality:french is on the right of Music-Genre:r&b##1
4. Music-Genre:indie is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:d&b is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:argentine is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | r&b    | d&b   | house       |
| Nationality   | argentine | pakistani | french | spanish |

