.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: iced-tea, water, fanta, 7up
Music-Genre: ambient, country, pop, classical
1. Beverage:iced-tea == Music-Genre:classical##1
2. Music-Genre:ambient is on the right of Beverage:iced-tea##1
3. Music-Genre:classical is between Music-Genre:ambient and Beverage:fanta##2
4. Beverage:iced-tea is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:classical is on the left or right of Music-Genre:ambient##3
6. Beverage:water is on the left or right of Music-Genre:country##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | fanta   | iced-tea | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | pop | country | classical        | ambient    |

