.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: juice, soy-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate
Food: onion, zucchini, pear, cauliflower
1. Food:zucchini is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:mirinda is on the left or right of Beverage:juice##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:pear is on the left of Food:cauliflower##1
5. Food:cauliflower is on the right of Beverage:juice##1
6. Food:pear is in an even position##4
7. Food:onion == Beverage:soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | juice    | mirinda       | soy-milk |
| Food       | zucchini  | pear | cauliflower | onion  |

